<li id="cite_note-15"><b><a href="#cite_ref-15" title="">^</a></b> R. E. Dunin-Borkowski et al., Micros. Res. and Tech. vol. 64, pp. 390-402 (2004)</li>
<li id="cite_note-16"><b><a href="#cite_ref-16" title="">^</a></b> K. Ogai et al., Jpn. J. Appl. Phys., vol. 32, pp.5988-5992 (1993)</li>
<li id="cite_note-holo-17"><b><a href="#cite_ref-holo_17-0" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFF.ShimizuJ.Fujita2002">F.Shimizu; J.Fujita (March 2002). "<a href="http://prola.aps.org/abstract/PRL/v88/i12/e123201" class="external text" title="http://prola.aps.org/abstract/PRL/v88/i12/e123201" rel="nofollow">Reflection-Type Hologram for Atoms</a>". <i><a href="/wiki/Physical_Review_Letters" title="Physical Review Letters">PRL</a></i> (<a href="/wiki/American_Physical_Society" title="American Physical Society">American Physical Society</a>) <b>88</b> (12): 123201. <a href="/wiki/Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<span class="neverexpand"><a href="http://dx.doi.org/10.1103%2FPhysRevLett.88.123201" class="external text" title="http://dx.doi.org/10.1103%2FPhysRevLett.88.123201" rel="nofollow">10.1103/PhysRevLett.88.123201</a></span><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://prola.aps.org/abstract/PRL/v88/i12/e123201" class="external free" title="http://prola.aps.org/abstract/PRL/v88/i12/e123201" rel="nofollow">http://prola.aps.org/abstract/PRL/v88/i12/e123201</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Reflection-Type+Hologram+for+Atoms&amp;rft.jtitle=%5B%5BPhysical+Review+Letters%7CPRL%5D%5D&amp;rft.aulast=F.Shimizu&amp;rft.au=F.Shimizu&amp;rft.au=J.Fujita&amp;rft.date=March+2002&amp;rft.volume=88&amp;rft.issue=12&amp;rft.pages=123201&amp;rft.pub=%5B%5BAmerican+Physical+Society%5D%5D&amp;rft_id=info:doi/10.1103%2FPhysRevLett.88.123201&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fprola.aps.org%2Fabstract%2FPRL%2Fv88%2Fi12%2Fe123201&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Holography"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
